tps://lih.kg/1506061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n小弟睇完呢個po，分享左比淺藍屋企人，佢地問:<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩原因係令外資要經香港入中國，而唔直接入中國？<br />\n到底係成本/風險上有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:35:28.000Z","msg":"法制，營商投資限制。<br />\n<br />\n最重要係&ldquo;外匯管制&rdquo;同&ldquo;人民幣不能自由流通&rdquo;。資金自由進出，對投資者而言係最緊要。"},{"pid":"6ff3081da1981ad5cd0118f79979d5ae1d710259","tid":1507081,"uid":142566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:35:36.000Z","msg":"幫你推推"},{"pid":"99cc365b21ccb6497613bbecb519e09b8215667e","tid":1507081,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=0fd1af47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kZESP.jpg&h=ba0a90fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"916c7b9d354d25c5b5b54a32005642eb2948f6ab","tid":1507081,"uid":264992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"外資直接投資中國=玩命<br />\n<br />\n就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"d954c9682df7ea6b232a9f5d0ee8bd3e40b32e60","tid":1507081,"uid":97389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29068f2d97d6c9295b3a113fbff74795fb1c5918","tid":1507081,"uid":97389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fe1b95f10bedc0a4d9325885f604d05c4e165b87","tid":1507081,"uid":240814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"From 金融朋友，佢終於忍唔住寫兩句<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n小弟睇完呢個po，分享左比淺藍屋企人，佢地問:<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩原因係令外資要經香港入中國，而唔直接入中國？<br />\n到底係成本/風險上有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:35:28.000Z","msg":"法制，營商投資限制。<br />\n<br />\n最重要係&ldquo;外匯管制&rdquo;同&ldquo;人民幣不能自由流通&rdquo;。資金自由進出，對投資者而言係最緊要。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"當中国有朝一日真係完全開放市場，就係香港末日。<br />\n<br />\n不過支那做到再算。<br />\n<br />\n坦白講，自清中葉開始，西方世界其實最主要都係只求支那一樣嘢：開放市場，讓外資可以不受限自由投資。"},{"pid":"e4273e0009487441b0b7f8119b8e3a72c00d951d","tid":1507081,"uid":308840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:43:52.000Z","msg":"1. 大多數國際交易以美元結算或經美元結算，港元跟美元掛鉤方便管理cash flow同匯率，在港轉換人民幣比較容易。中國有外匯管制，直接投資嘅錢有機會有入冇出。到最後大家都係想起中國搵完錢匯返自己國家，但中國當然唔想你拎錢走。<br />\n2. 仲裁，國際合約要寫跟邊個司法地區嘅法律，好多時都係寫香港，因為香港跟英美一樣行普通法，中國行大陸法。合約跟大陸法隨時比人熔咗都唔知。"},{"pid":"3f50c39883fafbf7ed902f1329bc10a1b66a1360","tid":1507081,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:45:26.000Z","msg":"其實有班離地中產藍絲係知 但佢地立場係無論點搞事破壞就唔岩 好撚離地<br />\n一班就都明香港既獨特性 但比中共拉撚左去反送中等於反中 佢自己又係大陸落黎 身邊又一堆大陸人 局住反示威者 唔係佢自己都會好撚矛盾 因為由此至終比人標籤左做港獨同反中 所以有班on9親中局住藍"},{"pid":"c63d0d2628fad446228982850b3cb26fe57b3c99","tid":1507081,"uid":58738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:06:31.000Z","msg":"外資信香港法例多個大陸，不過香港嘅法例而家都出出哋事，香港d例其實冇乜太大問題，不過操作上面出晒事"},{"pid":"be45e9094ef731ebb29e3c5ba6b7e0787cf97635","tid":1507081,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:10:06.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集思廣益  對付白色恐怖嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506382\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506382</a>"},{"pid":"a623762a6d5b286dc330abefd4a8515b4bb0d03a","tid":1507081,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:10:50.000Z","msg":"走資"},{"pid":"14b798375cbfdb4836f5979636c1458858d8e3af","